reviewText: Brilliant work, this event. Fantastic DVD!

Only because this disk skips on my dvd player for my TV. I had to play it on my computer. You may want to get the shorter version of this CD if available and read his blogs because some of his materials there are covered on the DVD
This is a 'must see' because it is intelligent, enlightening, and accurately projects a comprehensive view.  Money well spent!
Bought through amazon.  Got here quickly, and I enjoyed the DVD.

I like Armstrong. His views are spot on. He purports to give the average person information they can use, then prices his materials out of reach for the average Joe. His metals reports on his site look like they could help a lot of people who can't afford to buy it.
